    "scope_note": "Joseph Thomas Fowler's 1899 edited calendar and selection from eight Durham Cathedral Priory documentary groups, represented by the edition title page and printed pp. 285–576. It is not one medieval authored work, one manuscript, the complete surviving archive, or the complete three-volume Fowler publication. Historical records, Fowler's editorial compilation, the printed volume, the U-M encoding, and each physical object remain distinct layers."
